Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:26.09,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,エリクト
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:28.67,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,どうしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:29.95,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,どうしよう
